---
import BlogsBanner from "../../components/BlogsBanner.astro";
import MainLayout from "../../layout/Layout.astro";
const { frontmatter } = Astro.props;
---

<MainLayout>
  <BlogsBanner
    title="Make Your Qurbani Count This Year with My Sadaqah Online"
    image="/assets/images/blogs/make-your-qurbani-count-blog.jpg"
  />

  <!-- Blog content -->
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <!-- Blog header -->
    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-gray-500 my-6 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/logo-short.png"
            alt="Author"
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full mr-3"
          />
          <span
            >By
            <a
              href="#"
              class="text-teal hover:text-hotpink transition-colors duration-300"
              >My Sadaqah Online</a
            ></span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <i class="far fa-calendar-alt mr-2 text-teal"></i>
          <span>April 25, 2025</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <i class="far fa-clock mr-2 text-teal"></i>
          <span>5 min read</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Make Your Qurbani Count This Year with My Sadaqah Online</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Qurbani is more than just a ritual—it's an act of devotion, compassion, and care for others. As we prepare for Eid ul-Adha, many of us reflect on how to make our Qurbani truly meaningful. This year, let your sacrifice go beyond obligation and become a source of real impact.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            With <strong>My Sadaqah Online</strong>, your Qurbani can reach those who need it most—quickly, safely, and in accordance with Islamic guidelines.
          </p>
        </section>
      
        <!-- What It Means to Make Your Qurbani "Count" -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">What It Means to Make Your Qurbani "Count"</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Making your Qurbani count means giving with intention and ensuring your sacrifice brings genuine relief to others. It's about:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <li>Fulfilling your religious duty with sincerity</li>
            <li>Supporting communities where meat is a rare blessing</li>
            <li>Choosing a platform that ensures ethical and Shariah-compliant practices</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            When you choose to give through My Sadaqah Online, you're not just ticking a box—you're sharing your blessings in a way that matters.
          </p>
        </section>
      
        <!-- How My Sadaqah Online Delivers Real Impact -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">How My Sadaqah Online Delivers Real Impact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We work in some of the world's most vulnerable regions—places where poverty, hunger, and hardship are daily realities.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            By partnering with trusted local teams, <strong>My Sadaqah Online</strong> ensures your Qurbani meat reaches families who otherwise wouldn't have anything special for Eid. These include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <li>Widows, orphans, and refugees</li>
            <li>Low-income households in rural villages</li>
            <li>Conflict-affected and food-insecure areas</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Every sacrifice helps spread joy, dignity, and hope.
          </p>
        </section>
      
        <!-- Simple and Secure Qurbani Process -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Simple and Secure Qurbani Process</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Giving Qurbani through our platform is easy, secure, and stress-free:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <li><strong>Choose Your Animal</strong> – Cow, goat, sheep, or camel options available</li>
            <li><strong>Select a Location</strong> – Target your Qurbani to a region close to your heart</li>
            <li><strong>Make a Secure Payment</strong> – All transactions are protected and encrypted</li>
            <li><strong>Receive Confirmation</strong> – We'll keep you updated and informed throughout</li>
          </ol>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We also ensure that all animals are slaughtered humanely and in accordance with Islamic principles.
          </p>
        </section>
      
        <!-- Why Donors Trust My Sadaqah Online -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Why Donors Trust My Sadaqah Online</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Thousands of donors return to us each year because we focus on:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <li><strong>Transparency</strong> – You'll know where your Qurbani is going and who it's helping</li>
            <li><strong>Reliability</strong> – We've built a strong network of on-the-ground teams</li>
            <li><strong>Integrity</strong> – Every step is guided by ethics and Islamic values</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Our past campaigns have delivered Qurbani to people in need across Africa, Asia, and the Middle East—with powerful results and heartfelt gratitude from recipients.
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
